{"title":"Dynaplug Pill Celebrates Ten Years with Limited Edition Rasta Colors","link":"https://bikerumor.com/dynaplug-pill-celebrates-ten-years-with-limited-edition-rasta-colors/","date":1733841574000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" alt=\"(Photo / Dynaplug)\" /></p>\n<p>A decade ago, Chico, California’s <a href=\"https://shop.dynaplug.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Dynaplug</a> released The Pill. And today, to celebrate, Dynaplug releases a <a href=\"https://shop.dynaplug.com/products/dynaplug%c2%ae-pill-10-year\" target=\"_blank\">limited edition version</a> wrapped in Rasta colors. When the Pill first launched it quickly became a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/dynaplug-air-co2-tubeless-plugger-tool/\" target=\"_blank\">big favorite</a> of many cyclists.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"736\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880.webp\" alt=\"Dynaplug Pill Limited 10 Year Color first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880-297x171.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880-120x69.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-first-pic-jpeg-e1733767058880-768x442.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Dynaplug)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With its compact design, quality materials, and versatile plugging options, it’s no wonder the Dynaplug Pill became a preferred on-the-fly tubeless plug kit. The Pill was the first bicycle-specific tubeless repair tool on the market and is still a staple in many cyclists’ tool roll.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"582\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130.webp\" alt=\"Dynaplug Pill Limited 10 Year Color sitting merecat\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130-297x135.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130-120x55.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-sitting-merecat-jpeg-e1733767109130-768x349.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new limited “10-year Pill” is looking pretty fantastic all dressed in Rasta colors, I must say. The Pill is hand-anodized, so no two Pills will be the same. Machined from aluminum, the Pill weighs in at a scant 53g.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"503\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657.webp\" alt=\"Dynaplug Pill Limited 10 Year Color apart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657-297x117.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657-120x47.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Dynaplug-Pill-Limited-10-Year-Color-apart-jpeg-e1733767133657-768x302.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pop the Pill open and find that it includes the full suite of Dynaplug features. There are five plug-loaded insertion tubes, an air stopper, and a micro knife. This kit will repair most tubeless flats you may encounter out there, hassle-free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Dynaplug Pill Retail and Detail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $69 </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>USA-Made Machined Aluminum body</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Limited Edition</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Individually anodized, making every tool unique</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 – Dynaplug Pill tool</li>\n\n\n\n<li>5 – Insertion Tubes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 – Micro Knife</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 – Air Stopper</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 – Pipe Cleaner</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://shop.dynaplug.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Dynaplug.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/dynaplug-pill-celebrates-ten-years-with-limited-edition-rasta-colors/\">Dynaplug Pill Celebrates Ten Years with Limited Edition Rasta Colors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"425ed250d7a73b40fad68b7f2690a29c5e48fd6de90a54c7d88921c5d9020cf6","category":"Cycling"}